---
const caseStudy = {
  summary: "ðŸš€ Important discoveries! Sometimes spending too much time on documentation can take your focus away. Rethinking the client's premise about attracting a younger audience was key to improving the user experience. Do you want to know more? ðŸ‘€âœ¨ #UX #Design #Learnings",
  prototyp: "Methods used: Benchmarking. UX Analytics, Analysis of user engagement with Hotjar. Proto-persona by demographic segments. Key insights gained: A diverse audience of women who valued sustainability and product quality. Challenges were also identified such as lack of time, discrepancies in product images and doubts about sizes. In addition, the importance of an optimized shopping experience on mobile devices and a very active presence on social networks was highlighted.",
